Quickstrike:




Quickstrike held his shoulder while walking down the rest of the 
corridor, rounding to Black Arachnia's position. Cyber Claw walked 
behind him at a distance. They weren't happy with each other; 
Quickstrike recived an attack from Cyber Claw when he accidentily 
referred her to Dinobot. He didn't know that saying Cyber Claw wasn't 
Dinobot was a mistake.

Quickstrike had a dislocated shoulder from her and a scratch at his 
face. His shoulder really bothered him.

Cyber Claw was growling behind his back.
